This is an attempt to provide a TCP protocol model for OMNeT++. The
initial work has been done by Volker Boehm in 1999 with his diploma
thesis at the Institut fuer Nachrichtentechnik, Universitaet Karlsruhe
(T.H.) in Germany.

Any improvements are highly welcome.


